{"tid":1555271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好老實，唔俾錢地鐵賺先有用，扑爛野根本無用","createTime":"2019-09-09T09:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:49:57.000Z","uid":92811,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35e718f1283f749950151fb6b524919dc2d3ce86","tid":1555271,"uid":92811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"地鐵每年都預算左一筆天文數字既維修費，而呢筆數每年都要想盡辦法用哂去，唔可以留<br />\n<br />\n就算你地一日整爛幾部入閘機，都用唔哂呢筆錢，高層亦都唔會肉痛<br />\n<br />\n只有唔搭唔俾錢，盈利跌，先會減少高層花紅，佢地先會真正肉痛"},{"pid":"030051fd048e46b2f3835ed234d1efc5321e0936","tid":1555271,"uid":92811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f54368ec105f29098cf4c70f887b23fdf1c697","tid":1555271,"uid":82482,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"爛設施  封站   越封越多  越少人搭"},{"pid":"2e2d5f2fd52b1dd60c517dd26682f3407360519c","tid":1555271,"uid":60224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"可能又俾人話分化<br />\n明白大家都嬲,都想發洩<br />\n不過因為打爛一塊玻璃而開心<br />\n有用咩<br />\n精力同智慧應該用返係有效既方向"},{"pid":"5a78d08de48dc116d6ffead879cf21d5ebbbd4c9","tid":1555271,"uid":94494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"一帶一路峰會將在9月11-12日 在香港會展中心舉行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed8993829b6ce11b30e1e56e4374848618db3a84","tid":1555271,"uid":234271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:04:19.000Z","msg":"你望下個股價 <br />\n一個星期蒸發700億<br />\n爆多佢幾鑊就你咁先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽講廣告搵好多錢<br />\n大家千奇唔好爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839048f41fc9dff1a10868f6bd0ff2960720dbc7","tid":1555271,"uid":313546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"搞前線車站一樣無用。真係要搞就搞總部。